<refsect1 id="_description">
<title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<simpara>awesome-client is a remote command line interface to awesome.
It communicates with awesome via D-Bus, allowing remote execution of Lua code.</simpara>
</refsect1>
<refsect1 id="_usage">
<title>USAGE</title>
<simpara>awesome-client reads commands from standard input and sends them via D-Bus to awesome.
If <emphasis>rlwrap</emphasis> is installed, it will be used to provide a readline command line interface.</simpara>
<simpara>The <emphasis>awful.remote</emphasis> module has to be loaded if you want this command to work.</simpara>
</refsect1>
